       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. RPTGEN.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.
           SELECT REPORT-OUT ASSIGN TO "FINALRPT.TXT".
       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.
       FD REPORT-OUT.
       01 REPORT-LINE       PIC X(132).
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 WS-PAGE-COUNT     PIC 9(4) COMP-3.
       01 WS-LINE-COUNT     PIC 9(3) COMP-3.
       01 WS-DATE           PIC X(10).
       01 WS-HEADING.
          05 FILLER         PIC X(20) VALUE 'CUSTOMER REPORT     '.
          05 WS-HDR-DATE    PIC X(10).
          05 FILLER         PIC X(102) VALUE SPACES.
       01 WS-DETAIL-LINE.
          05 WS-DET-ID      PIC 9(8).
          05 FILLER         PIC X(2) VALUE SPACES.
          05 WS-DET-NAME    PIC X(30).
          05 FILLER         PIC X(2) VALUE SPACES.
          05 WS-DET-BAL     PIC ZZZ,ZZZ,ZZ9.99-.
       LINKAGE SECTION.
       01 LK-COUNTERS.
          05 LK-TOTAL       PIC 9(6) COMP-3.
          05 LK-PROCESSED   PIC 9(6) COMP-3.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING LK-COUNTERS.
       RPT-MAIN.
           OPEN OUTPUT REPORT-OUT.
           PERFORM WRITE-HEADING.
           PERFORM WRITE-TOTALS.
           CLOSE REPORT-OUT.
           GOBACK.
       WRITE-HEADING.
           MOVE 1 TO WS-PAGE-COUNT.
           WRITE REPORT-LINE FROM WS-HEADING.
       WRITE-TOTALS.
           MOVE LK-TOTAL TO WS-DET-ID.
           WRITE REPORT-LINE FROM WS-DETAIL-LINE.
           ADD 1 TO WS-LINE-COUNT.
           IF WS-LINE-COUNT > 55
               PERFORM WRITE-HEADING
               MOVE 0 TO WS-LINE-COUNT.
